261
00:16:27,691 --> 00:16:28,571
Yes.

262
00:16:28,943 --> 00:16:29,872
Between…

263
00:16:31,672 --> 00:16:33,800
Teacher Prince and

264
00:16:34,791 --> 00:16:36,229
Dr. Kuafah

265
00:16:38,178 --> 00:16:39,202
